 Introducing the Sigfred Chandelier Lighting Fixture. we like this lamp style because it utilizes a classical shape that has withstood the test of time. We love its perseverance. Blending into any environment while still purposeful and fitting in. This luminaire adds style and coziness to any room. 
 This dimmable pendant draws on sleek mid-century silhouettes and industrial overhead lighting to spotlight your space. The teardrop-shaped steel shade features a reflective inner finish for contrast plus warmth. Suitable for damp locations, it can even brighten a bathroom or covered porch. 
 The assembly is very simple and does not require any skill other than connecting parts together. You won’t have to use glue, nails or other messy products. Simply join all the pieces. 
 Be disruptive, let us fade into your space!

 Do you want to add a touch of luxury to your home but don't want to break the bank? Then look no further than our outdoor/indoor 10 ft. plug-in type bulb led string light with clear glass shades! Not only is this light perfect for adding a touch of elegance to any room, but it's also sustainable and eco-friendly - making it a great choice for anyone looking to make a positive impact on the environment. Plus, you can be sure that this light is both unique and stylish - perfect for any room in your home- indoors or out! 
 The set includes one 10-foot strand, each strand contains eight globe shades and LED light bulbs. These string lights will add a warm glow to interior or exterior spaces, creating the perfect ambiance for your home. Use as a single strand or connect up to four strands for larger areas. The bulbs look great with the lights on or off, providing a unique and trendy focal point during the day and at night. This set is ideal for porches and backyard patio spaces, or can be used for decorative lighting in bedrooms, living spaces, and more.
